{"tid":2431753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中芯國際獲美國鬆手，獲批部份供應許可，重生","createTime":"2021-03-04T01:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T12:15:03.000Z","uid":198316,"like":7,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"baf0311b4c2581ab83f903431e7a5cfd96af6c9a","tid":2431753,"uid":198316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:07:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%8D%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%AC%86%E6%89%8B-%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F-175658659.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258A%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25AC%2586%25E6%2589%258B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F-175658659.html&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=073bf28d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%8D%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%AC%86%E6%89%8B-%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F-175658659.html</a><br />\n在去年轟轟烈烈的中美貿易戰中，中芯國際也被美國列入了實體清單，高階晶片設備的製造和生產都受到了相當大的限制。<br />\n<br />\n直到近期，摩根士丹利研報稱，美國設備供應商已經開始恢復對中芯國際的零組件供應和現場服務。這對於技術受阻的中芯國際來說，其未來前景進一步明朗。<br />\n<br />\n在去年12月20日，中芯國際對列入美國實體清單的事情表態稱，「適用於美國《出口管制條例》的產品或技術，供應商必須首先獲得美國商務部的出口許可，才能供應給中芯國際」。<br />\n<br />\n美國對技術出口限制相當嚴格，特別是針對重要的技術節點，例如10nm及以下的產品或者技術，美國商務部會直接採取「推定拒絕」(Presumption of Denial)的政策進行審核。這導致在一些特殊的代工條件中，中芯國際將無法滿足需求。<br />\n<br />\n據消息中芯國際已經獲得了 14nm 及 28nm 等設備的供應許可。這對於中芯國際來說是一次重大的翻身。反觀此前中芯國際一直申請用於 14nm 工藝的設備沒有通過，這一次大方的一併通過了。<br />\n<br />\n雖然美國放寬了技術封鎖，但在尖端科技領域如 10nm、7nm、5nm 中芯依然無能為力。<br />\n<br />\n所謂兩黨共識真係笑話黎<br />\nIntel都係用緊14nm咋<br />\n你解唔解封中共都造唔到14nm以下架啦"},{"pid":"6cb662d026a74b0301b62feeb9c3e20931be140a","tid":2431753,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1323ecfccc92d1120db2e766419a0628a5cf7ed","tid":2431753,"uid":301820,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:28:32.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識<br />\n<br />\n共產黨同民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2df3c001ac62d9fd34de5ec7bda3065a13afc7d","tid":2431753,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:28:53.000Z","msg":"我記得Smic掘左好多台積電既人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人有設備有咩冇可能"},{"pid":"ddef8f6c60cbf3cd1492aac3254ba0e5e9575fb4","tid":2431753,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:31:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">China Joe<br />\n<br />\nmake China great again</span>"},{"pid":"4800d1bafed1ce74f6509791dd6b56153c61acaf","tid":2431753,"uid":35347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"所以intel製程咪垃圾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd5b0d7368f33b76374e0f357f22b6e69c77a0d","tid":2431753,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be65b87eb626f5f2ec1dffb46602a7a55ca41f1","tid":2431753,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"兩黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207d17fe8c36df8e0c72210bc17d697723b40823"